description.en-us: Virtual Garage (named NFT Garage until 2024) is a Hot Wheels series introduced in 2022 . Users of the platform may purchase non-fungible tokens (NFT) of Hot Wheels cars in packs of between three cars and ten. NFTs are divided into five rarities: Base, Rare, Premium, NFTH and Showroom, with those who receive Premium or NFTH rarity cars from these packs being able to redeem them for physical Hot Wheels models using a "redemption token". The series initially ran on the Worldwide Asset Exchange (WAX) platform before switching to Flow beginning with Series 4. The line was discontinued after Series 10.
